# Useful commands

/op/opt/zookeeper-3.4.9
## Starting zk	SERVER
./bin/zkServer.sh start [configuration file - default ./conf/zoo.cfg]


## Finish zk SERVER
./bin/zkServer.sh stop [configuration file - default ./conf/zoo.cfg]


## Connecting to client
./bin/zkCli.sh -server [IP1:PORT1] [, IP2:PORT2]


# PORTS=> Update configuration about replica:Lider election
# server.1=10.10.2.138:8080:80


### Inside the client
ls [path use '/' for root]
create [path] [value]
addauth digest [user:pwd]


